 {\"ngram\": \"a propos\\u00e9 que les\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"soient\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"de porter une jupe pendant les comp\\u00e9titions\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cette proposition a \\u00e9t\\u00e9rejet\\u00e9epar les boxeuses du monde entier.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\", \"score\": 0.997609014051072, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cette\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\u00e9t\\u00e9rejet\\u00e9epar les\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"entier\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bien que la question soit rest\\u00e9e en suspens jusqu'enjanvier 2012, il a finalement \\u00e9t\\u00e9 annonc\\u00e9 au printemps 2012 que les boxeuses seraient autoris\\u00e9es \\u00e0 choisir de concourir en jupe ou en short.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"soit rest\\u00e9e\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"suspens\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"a finalement \\u00e9t\\u00e9 annonc\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"2012 que les boxeuses\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"autoris\\u00e9es \\u00e0 choisir de concourir\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"jupe\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aujourd'hui, les principaux enjeux sociaux pour la boxe f\\u00e9minine aux Jeux olympiques portent sur la sous-repr\\u00e9sentation des femmes dans les r\\u00f4les d'entra\\u00eeneur et de leadership, ainsi que sur le manque de recherche concernant la pr\\u00e9valence du harc\\u00e8lement et des abus sexuels dans le milieu de la boxe.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2509, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abus_gun\", \"score\": 0.9999930666476099, \"rank\": 6.932237409715013e-06, \"text\": \"abus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abus_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abus_gun\"}, {\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milieu_(organized_crime_in_France)\", \"score\": 0.99999997490977, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"le milieu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milieu_(organized_crime_in_France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milieu_(organized_crime_in_France)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aujourd'hui\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"la boxe f\\u00e9minine\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"portent sur\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"les\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"d'entra\\u00eeneur et de leadership\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2615}]}, {\"sentence\": \